  <description>
    <p>Privacy applet for indicating when the microphone, camera or screen are being shared.</p>
    <p>The Flatpak version is currently unable to monitor the camera due to the sandboxing restrictions over the procfs.</p>
    <p>This feature will be implemented in the future using inotify.</p>
    <p>If you want the full functionality, you can install from the other methods in the repository, however automatic updates are only supported for the Flatpak version.</p>
